<section class="hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="eyebrow">v2.0.0 · open source · educational</div>
    <h1>Twenty-five LLM analysts walk into a room <em>and vote on what to buy.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Quorai is a research sandbox for AI-driven investment analysis. A quorum of language-model
      agents — each impersonating the philosophy of a well-known investor — debates ticker
      signals, applies risk constraints, and produces a final buy / sell / hold decision.
      Nothing is ever actually traded.
    </p>
